description:
Adobe Firefly is your AI video, image & audio generator designed to bring your creativity to life, whether you are a content creator, designer or innovator. From AI-generated video to image and sound effects, Firefly gives you the speed and flexibility to create on your terms, with the confidence of commercially safe AI models trained on licensed content. In addition, new intuitive AI partner models ensure you have the right model to choose for any task.  

Lead the creative process with Adobe Firefly’s AI Image generator. Our intuitive interface and tools allow you to shape original content that reflects your style, vision, and voice. Whether you’re a professional designer, content creator or a beginner, you can use Firefly for anything from fast concepts to advanced generative AI creations.  

Create anything you can imagine with Firefly!  

Download today to start creating original AI image-generated content.   

TEXT TO IMAGE AI GENERATION AND CREATIVE TOOLS:  
AI image generator: create high-resolution, commercially safe images from a simple text prompt.  
AI image editing tools: add new content, replace the background, or even remove unwanted elements with Generative fill.  

AI VIDEO & AUDIO GENERATION  
Text to video: turn a text prompt into a video clip right from your phone. Choose from a range of resolutions and aspect ratios to meet your creative needs.  
Extend video edits & animation: add seamless motion and cinematic transitions when you edit and create videos.  
Image to video: Animate your own unique still images with dynamic motion and edits.  
Firefly isn’t just an AI video or image creator - but Firefly is a mobile content creation AI tool on your phone that will bring your imagination to life.  

WHY FIREFLY?  
Advanced AI generation tool for video editors, image editors, designers, and content creators to move from ideation to execution faster.  
Generate studio-quality content – AI video, image & audio generation – in seconds.  
Designed for digital artists, filmmakers, and AI creators, with an intuitive experience that lets you learn as you go.  
Firefly uses AI models trained on licensed content, giving creators confidence in every asset.  
Create projects on your phone and keep them going on the web: Firefly creations automatically sync with your Creative Cloud account to expand your creative experience.  
Choose from the industry's top AI partner models, all in one place.  

Who is Adobe Firefly for?  
Mobile-first creators: AI video effects and image generator tools for fast, on-the-go content creation.  
Graphic designers, digital artists, photo editors and creators: experiment with AI image generated visuals and enhanced workflows.  
Video editors and filmmakers: AI video generation, motion effects, sound effects and seamless video editing.  
Social media creators and marketers: create scroll-stopping videos, eye-catching images, and dynamic content.  

Join the next generation of video creators, photo editors, graphic designers, and digital artists using Firefly mobile to create studio-quality content with next-gen AI tools that are fast, intuitive, and commercially safe.

With Widgy, your home and lock screens become YOUR screens. Create any widget you can imagine to perfectly match your style. Get all the info you need, exactly how you want it, without the clutter.

• Easy Widget Creation •

You don’t need to be a pro designer. Just know what you want, and let your creativity flow. Add an element, pick a data source, throw on some effects, and place it where you want. Repeat until your widget is perfect, then assign it to a slot and drop it on your home screen. Voila!

The Widgy editor is super simple with just two parts: the preview and the layer list. Edit a layer to tweak its appearance and data. The live preview shows exactly how your widget will look, so no more back-and-forth.

• Everything You Need •

Widgy has all the elements and data sources you could ever need, from system info to weather. Display your data as text, charts, or whatever you like.

• No Limits •

Forget templates. With Widgy, everything is 100% customizable. It’s your widget, your way. The only limit is your imagination.

• Easy Sharing & Discovering •

Share your creations with friends or the entire Widgy community in just a few taps. Use a URL, QR code, JSON data, or a file. You can even publish it in the Explore section for everyone to see.

Need inspiration? Check out thousands of widgets in the Explore section, or join the Reddit (r/Widgy) and Discord communities to see what others have created.


NOTE: Widgy optionally integrates with Apple Health. This integration is used to display your data if you select one of those widget types. Permission for Widgy to access this data is controlled through the Apple Health app.

As with Health, all other permissions for Widgy are optional and are there just to show you the data you want to be displayed.
